tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Market_Research (
  research_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  research_title VARCHAR(255),
  research_description TEXT,
  customer_feedback TEXT,
  market_trends JSON
)

CREATE TABLE Market_Research_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    research_topic VARCHAR(255),
    research_date DATE,
    researcher_name VARCHAR(100),
    market_trend_analysis TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE AI_Analysis (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_date DATE,
    research_id INT,
    feedback_id INT,
    trend_prediction TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE,
  satisfaction_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerSatisfaction (
  satisfaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  satisfaction_level INT,
  feedback_id INT,
  satisfaction_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE MarketResearchData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    feedback TEXT
);
